- the default context is opened with ctrl+space, and contains:
  - open today - opens today's a.log page ... - only shows if not in today's log .
  - "DO SOMETHING!!!!!" (choose a template) - shows a list of templates from directly inside of each e.proj, ordered by the decreasing priority of each project (can contain more than one template) ...
    / - only shows if inside a b.rec surface page ...
    - choosing one merges the information from b.rec with the template (templating logic for later) ...
  - insert timestamp - inserts a timestamp dd.mm.yyyy hh:mm where cursor is in editor - only shows if in editor ...
  - open picker - opens picker in a new tab (client to be created) . - if not already in it ...
  - open zettelkasten - opens zettelkasten in a new tab (client to be created) . - if not already in it ...
  - open projects - opens projects in a new tab (client to be created) . - if not already in it ...
  - change to fibonacci mode ... - only if in monocle mode ...
  - change to monocle mode ... - only if in fibonacci mode ...
  - edit .options - opens prsnl.spc/.options in editor ... - if not already in it ...
*** actually, you can write in the main menu, whatever command you would place in add-clients ...
