- inside d.fami, when inside one, or even at the index of one, the sidebar shall be filled with the internal structure of this family ...
- inside e.proj, when inside one, you shall see all the b.rec in cache that are owned in metadata by this project(through name with dashes) . ordered by decreasing time ...
- the viewport shall happens just like it's done in editor ...
