- make "+ new template" responds to ctrl+enter by creating a template inside the project with whatever name is in prompt . like: "e.proj/my-project/template-one" . it shall use "e.proj/.templates" to show a menu of templates fo the user to choose .
* and make the priority level always be updated, for new and changed projects metadata ...


